        </div>
        <div class="pat-name">Rising Channel</div>
        <p>Higher highs &amp; higher lows within parallel trendlines. Buy the floor, target the ceiling.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pat bull fi">
        <div class="pat-sig">▲ Bullish</div>
        <div class="pat-chart" style="align-items:center">
          <div class="c" style="height:52px;background:var(--red)"></div>
          <div class="c" style="height:30px;background:var(--red)"></div>
